Steps:
[AUTH role=ORG_USER]
[GQL-OP valid_name]
  mutation {
    createOrganization(command: { name: "{{valid_org_name}}" }) {
      id
      name
    }
  }
[GQL-EXEC valid_name]
[GQL-CAPTURE valid_name.data.createOrganization.id → VALID_ORG_ID]
[GQL-OP xss_name]
  mutation {
    createOrganization(command: { name: "{{invalid_org_name}}" }) {
      id
      name
    }
  }
[GQL-EXEC xss_name]

[ACT] Click query editor → clear (Ctrl+A, Backspace)
[ACT] Type mutation with HTML in phone: mutation { updateContact(command: { id: "{{contactId}}" phones: ["<img src=x onerror=alert(1)>"] }) { id phones } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify HTML in phone rejected
[ACT] Clear editor → type mutation with <script> tag in phone: mutation { updateContact(command: { id: "{{contactId}}" phones: ["<script>alert(1)</script>"] }) { id phones } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify script tag in phone rejected
[ACT] Clear editor → type mutation with 65-char phone (exceeds MaxLength 64): mutation { updateContact(command: { id: "{{contactId}}" phones: ["11111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111"] }) { id phones } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify oversized phone rejected
[ACT] Clear editor → type mutation with valid phone: mutation { updateContact(command: { id: "{{contactId}}" phones: ["+1-555-0123"] }) { id phones } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify valid phone accepted
[ACT] Clear editor → type mutation with empty phones array: mutation { updateContact(command: { id: "{{contactId}}" phones: [] }) { id phones } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify empty array accepted

[ACT] Click query editor → clear (Ctrl+A, Backspace)
[ACT] Type mutation with XSS in city: mutation { updateMemberAddresses(command: { memberId: "{{memberId}}" addresses: [{ city: "<script>alert(1)</script>" line1: "123 Main St" countryCode: "US" countryName: "United States" }] }) { id } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify HTML in city rejected
[ACT] Clear editor → type mutation with XSS in line1: mutation { updateMemberAddresses(command: { memberId: "{{memberId}}" addresses: [{ city: "New York" line1: "<img onerror=alert(1)>" countryCode: "US" countryName: "United States" }] }) { id } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify HTML in address line rejected
[ACT] Clear editor → type mutation with valid address: mutation { updateMemberAddresses(command: { memberId: "{{memberId}}" addresses: [{ city: "New York" line1: "123 Main St" countryCode: "US" countryName: "United States" }] }) { id } }
[GQL] Click Execute (▶) or Ctrl+Enter
[READ] Read response — verify valid address accepted
